    <p>The social signs of depression include:</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Avoiding contact with friends and taking part in fewer social activities</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Neglecting your hobbies and interests</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Having difficulties in your home, work or family life</p>
